Artist Biography

Available in:

Composer of video games such as Populous: The Beginning, Dungeon Keeper 2, Duke Nukem: Total Meltdown but now going back to my Amiga roots and reviving the name TDK to write those classic sounding chiptunes I became best known for on the Amiga demoscene.
